>   1a) If he starts into organized crime on his own, the mob
>will either recruit him or squash him flat before the police 
>do. Does organized crime have "standards" or "rules" for who 
>works for them? On a world with a high law level, what would 
>those be, and what kind of arrangements would let the mob
